ital decay as\n$\\dot{P}_{\\rm{orb}}/P_{\\rm{orb}}=-3.380(6)\\times10^{-6}$ yr$^{-1}$. Finally, we\nreconfirm the detection of the superorbital modulation in the optical band and\nits coherence in phase with the X-ray modulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2019 04:48:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2019 14:05:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
