 for scientific\napplications and reproduces the sea water density in a narrower oceanographic\nrange of parameters with a root mean square devi-ation of 0.0018 kg/m3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2019 12:55:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
